\displaystyle\lim_{x\to\frac{\pi}{4}^{-}} \frac{1}{\cot{x}-1}=\infty
\displaystyle\lim_{x\to\frac{\pi}{4}^{+}} \frac{1}{\cot{x}-1}=-\infty
